{"tid":209122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國新假期啲圖真係有陣柒味","createTime":"2017-04-20T03:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T17:18:43.000Z","uid":31820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f17b1d986b0c076b956889815031d7e3dffee4d9","tid":209122,"uid":31820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:32:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">天文台</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">預想圖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n現時天文台只有YouTube、Twitter、微博、微信、土豆這5個社交平台，還未開設Facebook及Instagram。所以，社交媒體主任亦要從零開始，在這兩個社交媒體建立帳號。雖然大家還未知道日後天文台Facebook及Instagram的推廣方向，又可能像小記一樣，未符合申請條件，也可以試試製作一下Facebook預想圖～<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66H39C6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66H39C6.jpg&h=168aa9f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/977pf5W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F977pf5W.jpg&h=531b6256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">sources: <a href=\"http://www.weekendhk.com/lifestyle/%e5%a4%a9%e6%96%87%e5%8f%b0-%e8%8d%80%e5%b7%a5-%e7%a4%be%e4%ba%a4%e5%aa%92%e9%ab%94%e4%b8%bb%e4%bb%bb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2Flifestyle%2F%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e6%2596%2587%25e5%258f%25b0-%25e8%258d%2580%25e5%25b7%25a5-%25e7%25a4%25be%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e5%25aa%2592%25e9%25ab%2594%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e4%25bb%25bb%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=913f0238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.weekendhk.com/lifestyle/%e5%a4%a9%e6%96%87%e5%8f%b0-%e8%8d%80%e5%b7%a5-%e7%a4%be%e4%ba%a4%e5%aa%92%e9%ab%94%e4%b8%bb%e4%bb%bb/</a></span>"},{"pid":"49ed7d17662bfdcc39cec29dedd016a5d32b03c0","tid":209122,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:35:11.000Z","msg":"極邪惡天文台fb"},{"pid":"63973db44c3d82a0bce4ff1c19163